# CURRENT OPTIONS: LINUX, RS6K, SUN4SOL2, SUNMP, X86SOL2, ALPHA
#
# Note that these architecture variable names are the ones used to define
# the various architectures recognized by the Parallel Virtual Machine (PVM)
# library. 
